<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
This sample illustrates text editor by using SfRichTextBoxAdv control that is similar to the Windows Sticky Notes.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
The following screenshot displays the same.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph TextAlignment ="Center"><Image Source="Images\StickyNotes.png" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph>   

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}" FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">Features</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List FontFamily="Segoe UI" FontSize="12pt">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports viewing and editing simple text notes.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports for customizing background.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports cut, copy, and paste the text to and from the SfRichTextBoxAdv.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports drag and drop the rich-text to and from the SfRichTextBoxAdv.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports undo and redo editing operations.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

</FlowDocument>